textAnnotations.description:
READ ALL WARNINGS
DIRECTIONS ON CARTON
BEFORE USE. RETAIN CARTON /
FOR REFERENCE.
Juaypanbuy angy
Anti-diarrheal
asodin
(in each caplet)
Loperamide HCI 2 mg..
Use controls symptoms of diarrhea,
including Travelers' Diarrhea
Directions
drink plenty of clear fluids to help
prevent dehydration caused by diarrhea
• find right dose on chart. If possible, use
weight to dose, otherwise, use age.
Adults and children 12 years and over:
2 caplets after the first loose stool,
1 caplet after each subsequent loose stook
G8-09)
